description:
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be responsible for providing in depth, specialist information, reports and recommendations to support senior management in the decision making processes. You will play a key role in the long term strategic planning and business management of the Trust through, for example, the development of demand and capacity dashboards, market and benchmarking analyses and analytical support to large scale improvement projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to pro-actively support senior managers and clinicians through their analytical skills and knowledge of NHS information, performance and planning frameworks. You will need to be educated to degree level and show initiative and self-motivation along with excellent interpersonal skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;**Please note this is not a technical role**&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Samantha Cole - Senior Business Insight Analyst&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: samantha.cole20@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 01623 622515 ext 6803&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Additional contact information;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email: samantha.cole20@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
